                                     "match_impact_sensitivity":  "Match Impact Sensitivity",
                                     "fan_count":  "Fan Count",
                                     "description":  {
                                                         "potential":  "The higher this stat, the easier the player grows through training, and the higher their growth potential grade is shown.",
                                                         "stamina_recovery_min":  "Minimum value in the random daily stamina recovery range.",
                                                         "stamina_recovery_max":  "Maximum value in the random daily stamina recovery range.",
                                                         "stamina_cost_per_set_min":  "Minimum value in the random stamina cost range when playing a set. The actual cost is adjusted by match length.",
                                                         "stamina_cost_per_set_max":  "Maximum value in the random stamina cost range when playing a set. The actual cost is adjusted by match length.",
                                                         "stress_sensitivity":  "The higher this stat, the easier stress builds when rest is lacking, and the less stress is reduced by rest.",
                                                         "condition_baseline":  "The baseline that the player's natural condition rhythm returns toward.",
                                                         "condition_amplitude":  "The higher this stat, the more the natural condition rhythm swings above and below the baseline.",
                                                         "condition_period":  "Number of days for the natural condition rhythm to complete a cycle. Lower values make peaks and dips change more often.",
                                                         "condition_phase":  "Shifts the condition rhythm forward or backward on the calendar. Different values make good and bad condition days arrive at different times, even with the same period.",
                                                         "match_impact_sensitivity":  "Controls how strongly wins, losses, and POG change condition after a match. 50 is normal, 0 prevents the change, and 100 doubles it.",
                                                         "fan_count":  "Number of fans for this player. It is used for streaming viewers, merchandise sales, and player fan changes after matches."
                                                     },
